ZH: 我的母亲是我的法定监护人。
EN: My mother is my legal guardian.

ZH: 在法律上，监护人有责任保护未成年人。
EN: Legally, guardians have the responsibility to protect minors.

ZH: 作为监护人，她有权利做出孩子的教育决策。
EN: As a guardian, she has the right to make educational decisions for the child.

ZH: 这个孩子没有合法监护人。
EN: This child does not have a legal guardian.

ZH: 许多儿童福利机构提供监护人的支持和指导。
EN: Many child welfare agencies provide support and guidance for guardians.

ZH: 据报道，监护人未履行其责任而导致的儿童虐待案件有所增加。
EN: Reported cases of child abuse due to guardians not fulfilling their responsibilities have increased.

ZH: 她是我最亲密的监护人之一。
EN: She is one of my closest guardians.

ZH: 当父母没有能力履行监护人的责任时，法院会指定监护人。
EN: When parents are unable to fulfill their guardian responsibilities, the court may appoint a guardian.

ZH: 孤儿院负责为孤儿寻找稳定的监护人。
EN: Orphanages are responsible for finding stable guardians for orphans.

ZH: 这位母亲决定放弃其作为孩子的监护人的权利。
EN: This mother decided to relinquish her rights as the child's guardian.

ZH: 法律规定监护人必须遵守儿童权益。
EN: The law mandates that guardians must respect children's rights.

ZH: 一名好的监护人应该提供稳定的生活环境给孩子。
EN: A good guardian should provide a stable living environment for the child.

ZH: 这名青少年将被移交给临时监护人。
EN: The teenager will be handed over to a temporary guardian.

ZH: 他是这所孤儿院的法定监护人。
EN: He is the legal guardian of this orphanage.

ZH: 作为监护人，她必须保证孩子的安全和福祉。
EN: As a guardian, she must ensure the safety and well-being of the child.

ZH: 孩子的监护人应该给予他们支持和指导。
EN: The child's guardian should provide them with support and guidance.

ZH: 我希望能找到一个有责任心的监护人来照顾我的孩子。
EN: I hope to find a responsible guardian to take care of my child.

ZH: 政府会提供金钱援助给需要负担监护人责任的人。
EN: The government provides financial assistance to those who bear the responsibility of being guardians.

ZH: 作为法定监护人，他有责任为孩子提供养育的基本需求。
EN: As the legal guardian, he has the responsibility to provide the child with basic needs for upbringing.

ZH: 孤儿会被安置在有经验的监护人的家庭中。
EN: Orphans will be placed in experienced guardians' homes.

ZH: 法律规定监护人必须为被监护人提供适当的医疗保健。
EN: The law stipulates that guardians must provide appropriate healthcare for their wards.
